"title": "6188: immorality, nature of sexual",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6188: immorality, nature of sexual",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sexual behaviour which is contrary to God's law.</p>\n<h2>Sexual immorality is widespread in the world</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:9-1Cor5:10\">1CO 5:9–5:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor7:1-1Cor7:2\">1CO 7:1–7:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev9:21\">REV 9:21</a></p>\n<h2>The cause of sexual immorality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:19\">GAL 5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:19-Matt15:20\">MAT 15:19–15:20</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:21-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:21–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:17-Eph4:19\">EPH 4:17–4:19</a></p>\n<h2>The folly of sexual immorality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:32\">PRO 6:32</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:3-Prov5:5\">PRO 5:3–5:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov5:20\">PRO 5:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov6:26\">PRO 6:26</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual immorality brings punishment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:4\">HEB 13:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev20:10-Lev20:21\">LEV 20:10–20:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:16-Prov2:19\">PRO 2:16–2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov22:14\">PRO 22:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek16:38\">EZK 16:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:24-Rom1:27\">ROM 1:24–1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:5\">EPH 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5-Col3:6\">COL 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3-1Thess4:6\">1TH 4:3–4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:7\">JUD 1:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev21:8\">REV 21:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev22:15\">REV 22:15</a></p>\n<h2>Sexual immorality has no place in the Christian life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:3\">1TH 4:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:7\">1TH 4:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:20\">ACT 15:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts15:29\">ACT 15:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts21:25\">ACT 21:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom13:13\">ROM 13:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:9-1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:9–6:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:13-1Cor6:20\">1CO 6:13–6:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor10:8\">1CO 10:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:3\">EPH 5:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:5\">COL 3:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:16\">HEB 12:16</a></p>\n<h2>Forgiveness for sexual immorality</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor6:11\">1CO 6:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke7:36-Luke7:39\">LUK 7:36–7:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:3-John8:11\">JHN 8:3–8:11</a></p>",
